00:11:11.640 --> 00:11:18.599
paper. So, you just get really good at it. I'm much better at writing news articles fast and on

00:11:18.599 --> 00:11:24.599
deadline than feature articles because news has a kind of template, really. It's what they call

00:11:24.599 --> 00:11:28.039
the inverted pyramid. You know, you put the most important stuff first, who, what, where, when,

00:11:28.039 --> 00:11:33.239
